         <abstract id="aspace_afbdbed9178c6d0d41e627e9d9fc2233">The records consist of correspondence, memoranda, and news clippings documenting contract negotiations between Yale and Local 34, Local 35, and the police union; union organizing drives; and labor strikes.</abstract>
