      <arrangement id="aspace_c1f993d0b2da589e6a27db95a9d27d79">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by topic.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_6e4af9bcd4dd9a7a4a897065e0d2892d">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, memoranda, and news clippings documenting contract negotiations between Yale and Local 34, Local 35, and the police union; union organizing drives; and labor strikes.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
